{"Id":457427,"Title":"折翼之鹤四章","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"伯昏子","Context":"老树癯影，有乌围之。寒涧清秩，有箨飞之。遥嶂崚嶒，有云依之。折翼之鹤，何所归之。何摧我羽，何伤我翮。羽下如雪，翮垂如戟。相羊九回，思鸣皋泽。折翼之鹤，归之何夕。不能奋飞，长眄崖崿。栖遑以处，同于鴳雀。谁为浩歌，声震清廓。归之何夕，折翼之鹤。昔我往矣，沧海飘纵。今我来思，蒹葭倥偬。碾霜轧露，玉轮谁董。折翼之鹤，来诗人梦。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"1fa0e35477c029be8f907946674a7d62","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":4929636,"Sentence":"不能奋飞，长眄崖崿。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bú néng fèn fēi ，cháng miǎn yá è ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929628,"Sentence":"老树癯影，有乌围之。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lǎo shù qú ying ，yǒu wū wéi zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929629,"Sentence":"寒涧清秩，有箨飞之。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hán jiàn qīng zhì ，yǒu tuò fēi zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929630,"Sentence":"遥嶂崚嶒，有云依之。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yáo zhàng lǐng céng ，yǒu yún yī zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929631,"Sentence":"折翼之鹤，何所归之。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shé yì zhī hè ，hé suǒ guī zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929632,"Sentence":"何摧我羽，何伤我翮。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hé cuī wǒ yǔ ，hé shāng wǒ hé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929633,"Sentence":"羽下如雪，翮垂如戟。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǔ xià rú xuě ，hé chuǐ rú ji ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929634,"Sentence":"相羊九回，思鸣皋泽。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiāng yáng jiu huǐ ，sāi mǐng gāo zé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929635,"Sentence":"折翼之鹤，归之何夕。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shé yì zhī hè ，guī zhī hé xī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4929